<h1>Meet your AI coach, <%= @user.name %>!</h1>

<p>Did you know Entmoot has a built-in AI coach to help you create better goals?</p>

<p>Our AI coach can help you:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Refine your goals</strong> - Get suggestions to make them more specific and achievable</li>
  <li><strong>Identify obstacles</strong> - Anticipate challenges before they happen</li>
  <li><strong>Create milestones</strong> - Break big goals into manageable steps</li>
  <li><strong>Improve your SMART criteria</strong> - Ensure your goals are truly actionable</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>How to use it:</strong></p>
<p>When creating or editing a goal, look for the "Refine with AI" button. Click it, and your AI coach will analyze your goal and offer personalized suggestions.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @app_url %>" class="button">Try the AI Coach</a>
</p>

<p>Think of it as having a personal coach available 24/7, helping you set goals that you'll actually achieve.</p>
